The President...

1650
01:17:07,090 --> 01:17:08,591
I know,
I know, George.

1651
01:17:08,624 --> 01:17:09,759
That's marvelous.

1652
01:17:09,793 --> 01:17:11,194
Commander Harry Bailey!

1653
01:17:11,227 --> 01:17:13,797
Mr. Gower, look at this,
the second page.

1654
01:17:13,830 --> 01:17:15,131
Now, look,
this is for you.

1655
01:17:15,164 --> 01:17:16,666
This is for you.
That's for you.
Okay.

1656
01:17:16,700 --> 01:17:19,302
ERNIE: Right, right, thanks.
See you again.

1657
01:17:19,335 --> 01:17:22,271
Hey! Be sure you
spell the name right.

