1672
01:17:56,039 --> 01:17:57,807
What did they
have to eat?
What'd they have to eat?

1673
01:17:57,841 --> 01:17:59,308
Uh, Harry,

1674
01:17:59,342 --> 01:18:02,511
you should see
what they're cooking up
in the town for you.

1675
