ERNIE: Harry Bailey!

2703
02:08:11,251 --> 02:08:13,720
George, you old son of a gun.

2704
02:08:13,754 --> 02:08:16,222
Harry. Harry.

2705
02:08:16,256 --> 02:08:17,791
Looks like I got here
too late.

2706
02:08:17,824 --> 02:08:20,193
Mary, I got him here
from the airport
just as quick as I could.

2707
02:08:20,226 --> 02:08:22,062
The fool flew
all the way up here
in a blizzard.

2708
02:08:22,095 --> 02:08:23,797
Harry,
how about your banquet
in New York?

2709
02:08:23,830 --> 02:08:25,098
Oh, I left right
in the middle of it

2710
02:08:25,131 --> 02:08:26,466
as soon as I got
Mary's telegram.

2711
02:08:26,499 --> 02:08:28,701
Good idea, Ernie.
A toast

2712
02:08:28,735 --> 02:08:31,972
to my big brother, George,
the richest man in town!

2713
02:08:32,005 --> 02:08:34,140
(ALL CHEERING)

2714
